 page optimizations' => 'Dèan comas air optimizations duilleag cairt','Display the cart page with a layout similar to the checkout page.' => 'Seall duilleag na cairt le cruth coltach ris an duilleag pàighidh.','Header and footer' => 'Ceann-cinnidh agus bonn-coise','Header and footer template' => 'Teamplaid header and footer','Controls whether to use the distraction free page header and footer or keep the currently active theme\'s header and footer.' => 'Smachd air am bu chòir bann-cinn is bonn-coise na duilleige gun dragh a chleachdadh no bann-cinn is bonn-coise a’ chuspair a tha gnìomhach an-dràsta a chumail.','Distraction free header and footer' => 'Header agus bonn-coise gun dragh sam bith','Theme\'s header and footer' => 'Bun-cinn is bonn a’ chuspair','Cart elements' => 'Feartan cairt','Make the order summary stay visible on the cart page while scrolling' => 'Dèan geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh ri fhaicinn air duilleag na cairt fhad ‘s a sgrìobhas tu','Coupon codes' => 'Còdan coupon','Select position where to display the coupon codes section on the cart page. Only applicable when AJAX cart and the integrated coupon codes in the checkout page are enabled.' => 'Tagh suidheachadh far an seall thu an roinn còdan cùpain air duilleag na cairt. Chan eil e iomchaidh ach nuair a tha cairt AJAX agus na còdan coupon amalaichte air an duilleag pàighidh air an comasachadh.','Hidden' => 'Falaichte','Before the cart items section' => 'Ron roinn stuthan cairt','Inside the cart items section' => 'Taobh a-staigh roinn stuthan cairt','After the cart items section' => 'Às deidh earrann nan nithean cairt','Before the shipping section' => 'Ron roinn luingeis','After the shipping section' => 'Às deidh an roinn luingeis','Before the order summary' => 'Mus deach an òrdugh geàrr-chunntas','Inside the order summary' => 'Taobh a-staigh an òrdugh geàrr-chunntas','Before the order totals' => 'Mus tig an òrdugh gu h-iomlan','After the order totals' => 'Às deidh an òrdugh iomlan','After the order summary' => 'Às deidh geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh','Shipping' => 'Luingearachd','Select position where to display the shipping costs and calculator on the cart page.' => 'Tagh suidheachadh far an seall thu na cosgaisean luingeis agus an àireamhair air duilleag na cairt.','Display as a cart section' => 'Taisbeanadh mar roinn cairt','Cross-sells' => 'Crois-reic','Select position where to display the cross-sells section on the cart page.' => 'Tagh suidheachadh far an seall thu an roinn tar-reic air duilleag na cairt.','Before the cart actions' => 'Ro ghnìomhan a &#39;chairt','After the cart actions' => 'Às deidh na gnìomhan cairt','Layout of cross-sell items on the cart page.' => 'Cruth de nithean tar-reic air duilleag na cairt.','Optimized horizontal cross-sells layout' => 'Cruth tar-reic còmhnard as fheàrr','Theme\'s cross-sells layout' => 'Tha cruth tar-reic a’ chuspair','Number of cross-sell items to display on the cart page' => 'An àireamh de nithean tar-reic ri thaisbeanadh air duilleag na cairt','Trust symbols &amp; badges' => 'Ìomhaighean earbsa &amp; bràistean','Add widget areas to the cart page' => 'Cuir raointean widget ri duilleag na cairt','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the cart page.' => 'Tha na raointean widget seo air an cleachdadh gus samhlaidhean earbsa agus bràistean earbsa a chuir air duilleag na cairt.','Checkout' => 'Dèan sgrùdadh air','Layout &amp; design' => 'Cruth &amp; dealbhadh','Checkout layout' => 'Cruth an t-seic','Design template' => 'Teamplaid dealbhadh','General styles for the checkout steps, order summary and other sections. Might also apply to other pages such as the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages.' => 'Stoidhlichean coitcheann airson na ceumannan pàighidh, geàrr-chunntas òrdugh agus earrannan eile. Dh’ fhaodadh e cuideachd a bhith a’ buntainn ri duilleagan eile leithid na duilleagan Cairt, Òrdugh a fhuaireadh agus Faic Òrdugh.','Dark mode' => 'Modh dorcha','Enable dark mode' => 'Dèan comas air modh dorcha','Header and footer templates' => 'Teamplaidean header and footer','We recommend using the distraction free header and footer to avoid distractions at the checkout page. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Read the research about cart abandonment</a>.' => 'Tha sinn a’ moladh a bhith a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn is bonn-coise gun aire gus nach cuir thu dragh air an duilleag pàighidh. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Leugh an rannsachadh mu bhith a’ trèigsinn chairtean</a> .','Logo image' => 'Dealbh suaicheantas','Choose an image to be displayed on the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Tagh dealbh a thèid a thaisbeanadh air bann-cinn na duilleige pàighidh. Chan eil seo a’ buntainn ach nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn is bonn-coise gun dragh.','Header background color' => 'Dath cùl-cinn a’ chinn','Choose a background color for the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Tagh dath cùl-fhiosrachaidh airson bann-cinn duilleag pàighidh. Chan eil seo a’ buntainn ach nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn is bonn-coise gun dragh.','HTML color value. ie: #f3f3f3' => 'Luach dath HTML. ie: #f3f3f3','Page background color' => 'Dath cùl na duilleige','Choose a background color for the checkout page. Color is applied to the <em>body</em> element.' => 'Tagh dath cùl-raoin airson an duilleag pàighidh. Tha dath air a chur ris an eileamaid <em>bodhaig</em> .','Footer background color' => 'Dath cùl-raoin footer','Choose a background color for the checkout page footer. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Tagh dath cùl-fhiosrachaidh airson bonn-coise na duilleige pàighidh. Chan eil seo a’ buntainn ach nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn is bonn-coise gun dragh.','Checkout elements' => 'Feartan checkout','Progress bar' => 'Bàr adhartais','Display the checkout progress bar when using multi-step checkout layout' => 'Seall am bàr adhartais pàighidh nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh cruth pàighidh ioma-cheum','Make the checkout progress bar stay visible while scrolling' => 'Dèan am bàr adhartais pàighidh ri fhaicinn fhad ‘s a sgrìobhas tu','Express checkout' => 'Express checkout','Enable the express checkout section' => 'Dèan comas air an roinn pàighidh luath','Displays the express checkout section at checkout when supported payment gateways have this feature enabled.' => 'A’ taisbeanadh an roinn pàighidh luath aig àite-pàighidh nuair a bhios am feart seo air a chomasachadh le geataichean pàighidh le taic.','Display express checkout buttons in one line for larger screens' => 'Seall putanan pàighidh luath ann an aon loidhne airson scrionaichean nas motha','Ignore additional checkout required fields when paying with a compatible express checkout payment gateway' => 'Na cuir a-mach raointean pàighidh a bharrachd a tha a dhìth nuair a phàigheas tu le geata pàighidh pàighidh luath co-fhreagarrach','Make the order summary stay visible while scrolling' => 'Dèan geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh ri fhaicinn fhad ‘s a sgrìobhas tu','Choose a background color for the order summary section.' => 'Tagh dath cùl-raoin airson earrann geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh.','Highlight the order totals row in the order summary table' => 'Comharraich sreath iomlan an òrduigh anns a’ chlàr geàrr-chunntas òrduigh','Most useful when the order summary section does not have a highlighted background color. Might also apply to the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages when using Fluid Checkout PRO.' => 'Nas fheumaile nuair nach eil dath cùl-raoin comharraichte air an roinn geàrr-chunntas òrduigh. Dh’ fhaodadh e cuideachd a bhith a’ buntainn ris na duilleagan Cart, Òrdugh a fhuaireadh agus Faic Òrdugh nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh Fluid Checkout PRO.','Action link on the order summary at checkout.' => 'Ceangal gnìomh air geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh aig àite-pàighidh.','Edit cart link' => 'Deasaich ceangal cairt','Cart items count' => 'Bidh nithean cairt a’ cunntadh','Link to shop page' => 'Ceangal gu duilleag na bùtha','Cart items' => 'Feartan cairt','Enable options to edit cart items on the checkout page' => 'Dèan comas air roghainnean airson rudan cairt a dheasachadh air an duilleag pàighidh','Allow customers to change product quantities or removing items directly at the checkout page.' => 'Leig le luchd-ceannach meudan toraidh atharrachadh no stuthan a thoirt air falbh gu dìreach air an duilleag pàighidh.','Hide cart items errors at the checkout page' => 'Falaich mearachdan nithean cairt aig an duilleag pàighidh','Do not display the cart items errors message at the top of the checkout page. When submitting the checkout form to complete the purchase, these error messages will always be displayed.' => 'Na seall teachdaireachd mhearachdan nithean na cairt aig mullach na duilleige pàighidh. Nuair a chuireas tu a-steach am foirm pàighidh gus an ceannach a chrìochnachadh, bidh na teachdaireachdan mearachd sin an-còmhnaidh air an taisbeanadh.','Place order' => 'Cuir òrdugh','Define the position to display "Place order" and terms checkbox section.' => 'Mìnich an suidheachadh airson “òrdugh àite” a thaisbeanadh agus teirmean earrann bogsa sgrùdaidh.','Some options might not be compatible with some plugins and themes.' => 'Is dòcha nach bi cuid de roghainnean co-chòrdail ri cuid de plugins agus cuspairean.','Below the payment section' => 'Fon roinn pàighidh','Below the order summary' => 'Gu h-ìosal tha geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh','Both below the payment section and the order summary' => 'An dà chuid fon roinn pàighidh agus geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh','Add widget areas to the checkout page' => 'Cuir raointean widget ris an duilleag pàighidh','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the checkout page.' => 'Tha na raointean widget seo air an cleachdadh gus samhlaidhean earbsa agus bràistean earbsa a chuir air an duilleag pàighidh.','Display checkout sidebar widgets only when viewing the last checkout step on mobile devices when using multi-step checkout layout' => 'Seall widgets bàr-taoibh dìreach nuair a choimheadas tu air a’ cheum pàighidh mu dheireadh air innealan gluasadach nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh cruth pàighidh ioma-cheum','Enable integrated coupon code section' => 'Dèan comas air roinn còd coupon aonaichte','Only applicable if use of coupon codes are enabled in the WooCommerce settings.' => 'Chan eil e iomchaidh ach ma tha cleachdadh còdan cùpain air a chomasachadh ann an roghainnean WooCommerce.','Display the coupon codes section title' => 'Seall an tiotal earrann còd coupon','Only applicable when coupon code is displayed as a separate section on the checkout or cart pages.' => 'Chan eil e iomchaidh ach nuair a tha còd cùpain air a thaisbeanadh mar earrann air leth air na duilleagan pàighidh no cairt.','Select position where to display the coupon codes section on the checkout page.' => 'Tagh suidheachadh far an seall thu an roinn còdan coupon air an duilleag pàighidh.','Before the checkout steps' => 'Ro na ceumannan pàighidh','As a substep before payment methods' => 'Mar fho-cheum mus dòighean pàighidh','As a substep after payment methods' => 'Mar fho-cheum às deidh dòighean pàighidh','Select style of the "apply coupon" button. Only applicable when the coupon code section is displayed "Before the checkout steps" on the checkout page, or "Before the cart items section" on the cart page.' => 'Tagh stoidhle a’ phutan “cuir a-steach coupon”. Chan eil e iomchaidh ach nuair a tha an roinn còd cùpain air a thaisbeanadh “Ron na ceumannan pàighidh” air an duilleag pàighidh, no “Ron roinn nithean cairt” air duilleag na cairt.','Default button style' => 'Stoidhle putan bunaiteach','"Add" link button' => 'Putan ceangail &quot;Cuir ris&quot;.','Checkout fields' => 'Àiteachan pàighidh','Optional fields' => 'Raointean roghainneil','Hide optional fields behind a link button' => 'Falaich raointean roghainneil air cùlaibh putan ceangail','It is recommended to keep this option checked to reduce the number of open input fields, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#1-address-line-2--company-name-can-safely-be-collapsed-behind-a-link" target="_blank">read the research</a>.' => 'Thathas a’ moladh gun cùm thu sùil air an roghainn seo gus an àireamh de raointean inntrigidh fosgailte a lughdachadh, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#1-address-line-2--company-name-can-safely-be-collapsed-behind-a-link" target="_blank">leugh an rannsachadh</a> .','Do not hide "Address line 2" fields behind a link button' => 'Na cuir am falach raointean “Seòladh loidhne 2” air cùl putan ceangail','Recommended only when most customers actually need the "Address line 2" field, or when getting the right shipping address is crucial (ie. if delivering food and other perishable products).' => 'Air a mholadh dìreach nuair a tha feum aig a’ mhòr-chuid de luchd-ceannach air an raon “Seòladh loidhne 2”, no nuair a tha e deatamach gum faigh iad an seòladh luingeis ceart (ie ma tha iad a’ lìbhrigeadh biadh agus toraidhean meatach eile).','Display the "Add" link buttons in lowercase' => 'Seall na putanan ceangail &quot;Cuir&quot; ann an litrichean beaga','Make the labels of optional field "Add" link button as <code>lowercase</code> (ie. "Add phone number" instead of "Add Phone Number"). This option also affects the link buttons for coupon code fields.' => 'Dèan na bileagan de raon roghainneil &quot;Cuir ris&quot; putan ceangail mar <code>lowercase</code> (ie. &quot;Cuir àireamh fòn&quot; an àite &quot;Cuir àireamh fòn ris&quot;). Bidh an roghainn seo cuideachd a’ toirt buaidh air na putanan ceangail airson raointean còd cùpain.','Billing address' => 'Seòladh airson cunntas','Select position where to display the billing address section on the checkout page.' => 'Tagh suidheachadh far an seall thu an roinn seòladh bileachaidh air an duilleag pàighidh.','As a step before shipping' => 'Mar cheum mus luingearachd','As a sub-step before the shipping address section' => 'Mar fho-cheum ron roinn seòladh luingeis','As a sub-step after the shipping address section' => 'Mar fho-cheum às deidh an earrann seòladh luingeis','As a step after shipping' => 'Mar cheum an dèidh luingeis','As a sub-step before the payment section' => 'Mar fho-cheum ron roinn pàighidh','Force billing and shipping addresses to the same (single section)' => 'Feachd bilean agus seòlaidhean luingeis chun an aon rud (roinn singilte)','Checkbox for "Same as shipping/billing address" checked by default' => 'Bogsa-dearbhaidh airson “Co-ionann ri seòladh luingeis / bileachaidh” air a sgrùdadh gu bunaiteach','The checkbox "Same as shiping address" will start as checked by default when the shipping address section is displayed first. <br>The checkbox "Same as billing address" will start as checked by default when the billing address section is displayed first. <br> It is recommended to leave this option checked as to significantly reduce the number of open input fields at checkout, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#3-default-billing--shipping-and-hide-the-fields-entirely" target="_blank">read the research</a>.' => 'Tòisichidh am bogsa sgrùdaidh “An aon rud ri seòladh luingeis” mar a chaidh a dhearbhadh gu bunaiteach nuair a thèid an roinn seòladh luingeis a thaisbeanadh an toiseach.<br> Tòisichidh am bogsa sgrùdaidh “An aon rud ri seòladh bileachaidh” mar a chaidh a dhearbhadh gu bunaiteach nuair a thèid an roinn seòladh bileachaidh a thaisbeanadh an toiseach.<br> Thathas a’ moladh an roghainn seo fhàgail fo sgrùdadh gus an àireamh de raointean inntrigidh fosgailte a lughdachadh gu mòr aig àm pàighidh, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#3-default-billing--shipping-and-hide-the-fields-entirely" target="_blank">leugh an rannsachadh</a> .','Highlight the billing address section in the checkout form' => 'Thoir cuideam air an roinn seòladh bileachaidh san fhoirm pàighidh','Shipping address' => 'Seòladh luingeis','Highlight the shipping address section in the checkout form' => 'Thoir cuideam air an roinn seòladh luingeis san fhoirm pàighidh','Shipping methods' => 'Dòighean luingeis','Choose in which position to display the shipping methods section.' => 'Tagh dè an suidheachadh airson an roinn dòighean luingeis a thaisbeanadh.','Before shipping address' => 'Mus tèid an seòladh a lìbhrigeadh','After shipping address' => 'Às deidh seòladh luingeis','Prevent automatic selection of the first shipping method' => 'Cuir casg air taghadh fèin-ghluasadach den chiad dhòigh luingeis','When enabled, the first shipping method available will not be automatically selected when no other shipping method was previously selected for each shipping package. <br>This option will be automatically enabled if the option for clearing the selected shipping method is enabled for the Local Pickup feature.' => 'Nuair a bhios e comasach, cha tèid a’ chiad dòigh luingeis a tha ri fhaighinn a thaghadh gu fèin-ghluasadach nuair nach deach dòigh luingeis sam bith eile a thaghadh roimhe airson gach pasgan luingeis.<br> Bidh an roghainn seo air a chomasachadh gu fèin-ghluasadach ma tha an roghainn airson an dòigh luingeis taghte a ghlanadh air a chomasachadh airson am feart Pickup Ionadail.','Local pickup' => 'Togail ionadail','Removes shipping address section when a local pickup shipping method is selected.' => 'Thoir air falbh roinn seòladh luingeis nuair a thèid dòigh luingeis togail ionadail a thaghadh.','Replaces the shipping address with the pickup point location when a local pickup shipping method is selected.' => 'Cuir àite an àite togail an àite an t-seòlaidh luingeis nuair a thèid dòigh luingeis togail ionadail a thaghadh.','Show option to clear shipping methods in the pickup location substep' => 'Seall roghainn gus dòighean luingeis a ghlanadh anns an fho-cheum àite togail','Show a link button on the pickup location substep to clear the chosen shipping methods. This can be used to allow showing the shipping address section again if a local pickup method was previously selected.' => 'Seall putan ceangail air an fho-cheum àite togail gus na dòighean luingeis taghte a ghlanadh. Faodar seo a chleachdadh gus an roinn seòladh luingeis a shealltainn a-rithist ma chaidh dòigh togail ionadail a thaghadh roimhe seo.','Choose which address to save as the shipping address for local pickup orders.' => 'Tagh dè an seòladh airson a shàbhaladh mar an seòladh luingeis airson òrdughan togail ionadail.','Save the selected pickup location' => 'Sàbhail an t-àite togail taghte','Save same as the billing address' => 'Sàbhail an aon rud ris an t-seòladh cunntais','Do not save any shipping address' => 'Na sàbhail seòladh luingeis sam bith','Company name field for shipping address' => 'Raon ainm companaidh airson seòladh luingeis','Change visibility for the company name field for the shipping address section on the checkout form.' => 'Atharraich faicsinneachd airson raon ainm a ’chompanaidh airson an roinn seòladh luingeis air an fhoirm pàighidh.','If field is set as "optional", which is the default visibility state, no changes will be applied to let other plugins apply any changes they need.' => 'Ma tha an raon air a shuidheachadh mar “roghainneil”, is e sin an staid faicsinneachd bunaiteach, cha tèid atharrachaidhean sam bith a chuir an sàs gus leigeil le plugins eile atharrachaidhean sam bith a tha a dhìth orra a chuir an sàs.','Hidden (remove field)' => 'Falaichte (thoir air falbh an raon)','Optional' => 'Roghainneil','Required' => 'A dhìth','Add shipping phone field to the checkout form.' => 'Cuir raon fòn luingeis ris an fhoirm pàighidh.','Choose in which step to display the shipping phone field.' => 'Tagh dè an ceum gus an raon fòn luingeis a thaisbeanadh.','Contact step' => 'Ceum fios','Billing phone' => 'fòn bileachaidh','Add billing phone field to the checkout form.' => 'Cuir raon fòn bileachaidh ris an fhoirm pàighidh.','Choose in which step to display the billing phone field.' => 'Tagh dè an ceum gus an raon fòn bileachaidh a thaisbeanadh.','Enable international phone number format and validation for phone fields' => 'Dèan comas air cruth àireamh fòn eadar-nàiseanta agus dearbhadh airson raointean fòn','Format and validate phone numbers according to each country.' => 'Cruth agus dearbhaich àireamhan fòn a rèir gach dùthaich.','Enable phone number validation based on country rules' => 'Dèan comas air dearbhadh àireamh fòn stèidhichte air riaghailtean dùthcha','When disabled, the phone field validation will not check if country or area codes are valid for the country.' => 'Nuair a tha e ciorramach, cha dèan dearbhadh an raon fòn sgrùdadh a bheil còdan dùthcha no sgìre dligheach airson na dùthcha.','Only show allowed countries for shipping or billing' => 'Na seall ach dùthchannan ceadaichte airson luingearachd no bilean','When enabled, only the countries allowed for shipping will be available in the shipping phone field, and only countries allowed for billing will be available for the billing phone field.' => 'Nuair a bhios e comasach, cha bhi ach na dùthchannan a tha ceadaichte airson luingearachd rim faighinn anns an raon fòn luingeis, agus is e dìreach dùthchannan a tha ceadaichte airson bilean a bhios rim faighinn airson an raon fòn bileachaidh.','Show country code beside the flag' => 'Seall còd na dùthcha ri taobh na brataich','Show an example of a valid phone number inside phone fields' => 'Seall eisimpleir de àireamh fòn dligheach taobh a-staigh raointean fòn','Do not change placeholders' => 'Na atharraich luchd-àite','Show if not defined' => 'Seall mura h-eil e air a mhìneachadh','Always show' => 'Seall an-còmhnaidh','Order notes' => 'Òrdugh notaichean','Define the visibility of the additional order notes field.' => 'Mìnich faicsinneachd an raon notaichean òrdugh a bharrachd.','Gift options' => 'Roghainnean tiodhlac','Display gift message and other gift options at the checkout page' => 'Seall teachdaireachd tiodhlac agus roghainnean tiodhlac eile air an duilleag pàighidh','Allow customers to add a gift message and other gift related options to the order.' => 'Leig le luchd-ceannach teachdaireachd tiodhlac agus roghainnean eile co-cheangailte ri tiodhlac a chur ris an òrdugh.','Display the gift message fields always expanded' => 'Seall na raointean teachdaireachd tiodhlac an-còmhnaidh air an leudachadh','Display the gift message as part of the order details table instead of a separate section' => 'Seall an teachdaireachd tiodhlac mar phàirt de chlàr mion-fhiosrachadh an òrduigh an àite earrann air leth','This option affects the order confirmation page (thank you page) and order details on account pages, emails and packing slips.' => 'Bheir an roghainn seo buaidh air duilleag dearbhaidh òrduigh (duilleag taing) agus mion-fhiosrachadh òrduigh air duilleagan cunntais, puist-d agus bileagan pacaidh.','Account matching' => 'Co-fhreagairt cunntais','Enable the account matching feature' => 'Dèan comas air feart co-ionnanachd cunntais','Associate the guest customer\'s orders with their existing account when an account already exists with the customer\'s contact details.' => 'Ceangail òrdughan an neach-ceannach aoigheachd leis a’ chunntas a th’ aca mu thràth nuair a tha cunntas ann mu thràth le fiosrachadh conaltraidh an neach-ceannach.','Display message when an account exists with the email address provided' => 'Seall teachdaireachd nuair a tha cunntas ann leis an t-seòladh post-d a chaidh a thoirt seachad','Replaces the account creation fields with a notification and option to log in. In some contexts, it might be recommended to leave this option disabled to protect the privacy of customers.' => 'Cuir brath agus roghainn logadh a-steach an àite nan raointean cruthachaidh cunntais. Ann an cuid de cho-theacsan, dh’ fhaodadh gum biodh e air a mholadh an roghainn seo fhàgail ciorramach gus prìobhaideachd luchd-ceannach a dhìon.','Dashboard' => 'Deas-bhòrd','Integrations' => 'Amalachaidhean','No integrations available at the moment on this section. The options related to each plugin will only appear here if that plugin is activated.' => 'Chan eil aonachadh ri fhaighinn air an roinn seo an-dràsta. Cha nochd na roghainnean co-cheangailte ri gach plugan an seo ach ma tha am plugan sin air a ghnìomhachadh.','License keys' => 'Iuchraichean ceadachais','No license keys options available at the moment on this section. The options related to each plugin or add-on will appear here when that plugin is activated.' => 'Chan eil roghainnean iuchair ceadachais ri fhaighinn an-dràsta air an roinn seo. Nochdaidh na roghainnean co-cheangailte ri gach plugan no tuilleadan an seo nuair a thèid am plugan sin a ghnìomhachadh.','Visit our website for more information about our plugins and add-ons.' => 'Tadhail air an làrach-lìn againn airson tuilleadh fiosrachaidh mu na plugins agus na tuilleadan againn.','Order pay page' => 'Duilleag pàighidh òrdugh','Order pay' => 'Òrdugh pàigheadh','Enable order pay page optimizations' => 'Dèan comas air òrdugh pàighidh duilleag optimizations','Changes the layout of order pay page for existing orders pending payment from the customer.' => 'Ag atharrachadh cruth duilleag pàighidh òrduigh airson òrdughan a th’ ann mar-thà a’ feitheamh ri pàigheadh bhon neach-ceannach.','Add widget areas to the order pay page' => 'Cuir raointean widget ris an duilleag pàighidh òrduigh','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the order pay page.' => 'Tha na raointean widget seo air an cleachdadh gus samhlaidhean earbsa agus bràistean earbsa a chuir air duilleag pàighidh an òrduigh.','Thank you page & order details layout' => 'Duilleag taing &amp; cruth mion-fhiosrachadh an òrduigh','Order details optimizations' => 'Òrdaich mion-fhiosrachadh optimizations','Enable thank you page and order details optimizations' => 'Dèan comas air duilleag taing agus òrduigh mion-fhiosrachadh optimizations','Changes the layout of order details on the thank you page and account pages.' => 'Ag atharrachadh cruth mion-fhiosrachadh òrduigh air an duilleag taing agus duilleagan cunntais.','Enable order details customizations on email notifications' => 'Dèan comas air gnàthachadh mion-fhiosrachadh òrduigh air brathan post-d','Display new sections and change order of sections on email notifications. Styles of order details on email notifications remain unchanged.' => 'Seall earrannan ùra agus atharraich òrdugh nan earrannan air brathan post-d. Tha stoidhlichean mion-fhiosrachadh òrduigh air brathan post-d fhathast gun atharrachadh.','Thank you page' => 'Tapadh leibh duilleag','These options affect the thank you page, also known as order received or order confirmation pages.' => 'Bheir na roghainnean sin buaidh air an duilleag taing, ris an canar cuideachd òrdugh a fhuaireadh no duilleagan dearbhaidh òrduigh.','Order details layout' => 'Òrdugh cruth mion-fhiosrachadh','Display the order details with wide layout on the thank you page' => 'Seall mion-fhiosrachadh an òrduigh le cruth farsaing air an duilleag taing','Add widget areas to the thank you page' => 'Cuir raointean widget ris an duilleag taing','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the thank you page.' => 'Tha na raointean widget seo air an cleachdadh gus samhlaidhean earbsa agus bràistean earbsa a chuir air an duilleag taing.','These options affect the thank you page , view order details on account pages and on email notifications.' => 'Bheir na roghainnean sin buaidh air an duilleag taing, faic mion-fhiosrachadh an òrduigh air duilleagan cunntais agus air fiosan post-d.','Order actions' => 'Òrdugh gnìomhan','Choose in which position to display the order actions.' => 'Tagh dè an suidheachadh gus na gnìomhan òrduigh a thaisbeanadh.','Inside the order overview' => 'Geàrr-chunntas taobh a-staigh òrdugh','After the order overview' => 'Às deidh geàrr-chunntas an òrduigh','After order sections' => 'Às deidh earrannan òrdugh','Order status' => 'Inbhe òrduigh','Display the order status progress bar' => 'Seall am bàr adhartais inbhe òrduigh','Choose in which position to display the section.' => 'Tagh dè an suidheachadh airson an roinn a thaisbeanadh.','After the order overview and payment instructions' => 'Às deidh ath-shealladh an òrduigh agus an stiùireadh pàighidh','Before the order items section' => 'Ro earrann nan nithean òrduigh','Inside the order items section' => 'Taobh a-staigh earrann nan stuthan òrduigh','After the order items section' => 'Às deidh earrann nan nithean òrduigh','On the sidebar' => 'Air a &#39;bhàr-taobh','Order downloads' => 'Òrdughan luchdadh a-nuas','Gift message' => 'Teachdaireachd tiodhlac','Tools' => 'Innealan','Troubleshooting' => 'Fuasgladh thrioblaidean','Debug options' => 'Roghainnean deasbaid','Debug mode' => 'Modh deasbaid','Using debug mode affects the website performance. Only use this option while troubleshooting.' => 'Bidh cleachdadh modh deasbaid a’ toirt buaidh air coileanadh na làraich-lìn. Na cleachd an roghainn seo ach fhad ‘s a tha thu a’ fuasgladh dhuilgheadasan.','Load unminified assets' => 'Luchdaich a-nuas maoin gun chlàradh','Enhanced select fields' => 'Raointean taghte leasaichte','Replace <code>select2</code> dropdown components with <code>TomSelect</code>' => 'Cuir <code>TomSelect</code> an àite co-phàirtean taghte <code>select2</code> a-nuas','TomSelect is a simpler dropdown selection component which is less prone to errors than Select2, while offering the same features that are actually used on WooCommerce checkout pages.' => 'Tha TomSelect na phàirt taghaidh tuiteam-sìos nas sìmplidh nach eil cho buailteach do mhearachdan na Select2, fhad ‘s a tha e a’ tabhann na h-aon fheartan a thathas a ’cleachdadh air duilleagan pàighidh WooCommerce.','Fix automatic zoom-in on form fields' => 'Ceartaich gluasad a-steach fèin-ghluasadach air raointean foirm','Set <code>font-size</code> inside form fields to 16px' => 'Suidhich <code>font-size</code> taobh a-staigh raointean cruth gu 16px','When the font size inside form fields is smaller than 16px, Safari and other browsers might automatically zoom in on mobile devices to make the text easier to read. When this option is enabled, it will set the font size for inside the form fields to 16px on pages optimized by Fluid Checkout to avoid it zooming in.' => 'Nuair a tha meud cruth-clò taobh a-staigh raointean cruth nas lugha na 16px, faodaidh Safari agus brobhsairean eile gluasad a-steach gu fèin-ghluasadach air innealan gluasadach gus an teacsa a dhèanamh nas fhasa a leughadh. Nuair a bhios an roghainn seo air a chomasachadh, suidhichidh e meud cruth-clò taobh a-staigh nan raointean foirm gu 16px air duilleagan air an ùrachadh le Fluid Checkout gus nach gluais e a-steach.','The shipping destination is always set to "Default to customer shipping address" when Fluid Checkout is activated. Customers can still provide different shipping and billing addresses during checkout, an option for setting the default billing address to be the same as the shipping address is available at WooCommerce > Settings > Fluid Checkout.' => 'Tha an ceann-uidhe luingeis an-còmhnaidh air a shuidheachadh gu “Default gu seòladh luingeis teachdaiche” nuair a thèid Fluid Checkout a chuir an gnìomh. Faodaidh luchd-ceannach fhathast diofar sheòlaidhean luingeis is bileachaidh a thoirt seachad aig àm pàighidh, tha roghainn airson an seòladh bileachaidh bunaiteach a shuidheachadh mar an aon rud ris an t-seòladh luingeis ri fhaighinn aig WooCommerce&gt; Settings&gt; Fluid Checkout.','Fluid Checkout' => 'Checkout fluid','Settings' => 'Suidhichidhean','Support' => 'Taic','<a target="_blank" href="%s">Upgrade to PRO</a> to unlock more options.' => '<a target="_blank" href="%s">Àrdaich gu PRO</a> gus barrachd roghainnean fhuasgladh.','(PRO)' => '(PRO)','(experimental)' => '(deuchainneach)','This is an experimental feature and may not work as expected with all themes and plugins. Use it with caution.' => 'Is e feart deuchainneach a tha seo agus is dòcha nach obraich e mar a bhiodh dùil leis a h-uile cuspair agus plugan. Cleachd e le cùram.','Confirm' => 'Dearbhaich','Verify Phone Number' => 'Dearbhaich àireamh fòn','Please verify your phone number.' => 'Feuch an dearbhaich thu an àireamh fòn agad.','The Bluehost Plugin' => 'Am plugan Bluehost','Custom fields' => 'Raointean gnàthaichte','Enable custom shipping email field' => 'Dèan comas air raon post-d àbhaisteach luingearachd','When enabled, the shipping email field from the Bluehost plugin will be added to the checkout form.' => 'Nuair a bhios e comasach, thèid an raon post-d luingeis bhon plugan Bluehost a chur ris an fhoirm pàighidh.','Captcha Pro by BestWebSoft' => 'Captcha Pro le BestWebSoft','Captcha position' => 'Suidheachadh captcha','Define the position to display the captcha section. Some positions might not work depending on the captcha type chosen.' => 'Mìnich an suidheachadh airson an earrann captcha a thaisbeanadh. Is dòcha nach obraich cuid de dhreuchdan a rèir an t-seòrsa captcha a chaidh a thaghadh.','Selecting a pickup point is required before proceeding.' => 'Feumar àite togail a thaghadh mus lean thu air adhart.','Pickup point' => 'Àite togail','Pickup point not selected yet.' => 'Chan eil puing togail air a thaghadh fhathast.','Pickup point:' => 'Àite togail:','Mailchimp for WooCommerce' => 'Mailchimp airson WooCommerce','Subscribe checkbox' => 'Subscribe box','Override the position for the subscribe checkbox on the checkout page and always display it on the contact step' => 'Cuir thairis suidheachadh a’ bhogsa sgrùdaidh ballrachd air an duilleag pàighidh agus an-còmhnaidh seall e air a’ cheum conaltraidh','Before Shipping Address' => 'Ro sheòladh Shipping','(originally "%s")' => '(&quot;%s an toiseach&quot;)','After Shipping Address' => 'Às deidh Seòladh Shipping','Selecting a collection point is required when shipping with FermoPoint.' => 'Tha feum air àite cruinneachaidh a thaghadh nuair a thathar a’ lìbhrigeadh le FermoPoint.','If checked informs typos in email to users. (This feature has been disabled because Fluid Checkout offers the feature. Changes to this option will not take effect)' => 'Ma thèid a sgrùdadh cuir fios gu typos ann am post-d gu luchd-cleachdaidh. (Chaidh am feart seo a chur à comas a chionn &#39;s gu bheil Fluid Checkout a&#39; tabhann am feart. Cha tig atharraichean air an roghainn seo gu buil)','Enable Mail Check: (disabled feature)' => 'Dèan comas air seic puist: (feart ciorramach)','Carrier:' => 'Neach-giùlain:','Sendinblue - WooCommerce Email Marketing' => 'Sendinblue - Margaidheachd post-d WooCommerce','Sign up checkbox position' => 'Clàraich suidheachadh a’ bhogsa sgrùdaidh','Move the sign up checkbox to the contact step' => 'Gluais am bogsa-dearbhaidh soidhnidh chun cheum conaltraidh','When enabled, the checkbox will be moved to the contact step independently of the display location defined in the Sendinblue plugin settings.' => 'Nuair a bhios e comasach, thèid am bogsa-dearbhaidh a ghluasad chun cheum conaltraidh gu neo-eisimeileach bhon àite taisbeanaidh a tha air a mhìneachadh ann an roghainnean plugan Sendinblue.','Theme Betheme' => 'Cuspair Betheme','Checkout progress' => 'Adhartas checkout','Output the checkout steps section from Betheme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Cuir a-mach an earrann ceumannan pàighidh bho Betheme air na duilleagan pàighidh, cairt agus òrdugh a fhuaireadh.','Theme Fennik' => 'Cuspair Fennik','Breadcrumbs' => 'Briosgaidean','Output the breadcrumbs section from the Fennik theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Cuir a-mach an roinn briseagan bho chuspair Fennik nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn is bonn-coise Fluid Checkout.','Theme Go' => 'Theme Rach','My account layout' => 'Cruth mo chunntas','Enable wide layout on "My account" page.' => 'Dèan comas air cruth farsaing air duilleag “Mo chunntas”.','Theme Impreza' => 'Cuspair Impreza','Header' => 'Ceann-cinnidh','Spacing for site header at the checkout page (in pixels)' => 'Àite airson bann-cinn na làraich aig an duilleag pàighidh (ann am piogsail)','Only applicable when using the Impreza theme header at the checkout page.' => 'Freagarrach a-mhàin nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn cuspair Impreza air an duilleag pàighidh.','Theme Kapee' => 'Cuspair Kapee','Output the checkout steps section from the Kapee theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Cuir a-mach an roinn ceumannan pàighidh bho chuspair Kapee air na duilleagan pàighidh, cairt agus òrdugh a fhuaireadh.','Theme Porto' => 'Porto cuspair','Output the checkout steps section from the Porto theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Cuir a-mach an roinn ceumannan pàighidh bho chuspair Porto air na duilleagan pàighidh, cairt agus òrdugh a fhuaireadh.','Theme Pressmart' => 'Cuspair Pressmart','Output the checkout steps section from the Pressmart theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Cuir a-mach an roinn ceumannan pàighidh bhon chuspair Pressmart air na duilleagan pàighidh, cairt agus òrdugh a fhuaireadh.','Theme The Gem' => 'Cuspair The Gem','Output the checkout steps section from The Gem theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Cuir a-mach an roinn ceumannan pàighidh bho chuspair The Gem nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn is bonn-coise Fluid Checkout.','Theme Woodmart' => 'Cuspair Woodmart','Output the checkout steps section from the Woodmart theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Cuir a-mach an earrann ceumannan pàighidh bho chuspair Woodmart nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh bann-cinn is bonn-coise Fluid Checkout.','Checkout options' => 'Roghainnean pàighidh','Disable the theme checkout options' => 'Cuir à comas roghainnean pàighidh cuspair','The options display product image, quantity field, remove button and link to product page added by the theme are disabled by default.' => 'Tha na roghainnean a’ taisbeanadh ìomhaigh toraidh, raon meud, putan thoir air falbh agus ceangal gu duilleag toraidh a chuir an cuspair ris a chiorramachadh gu bunaiteach.','Theme Atomion' => 'Atomion cuspair','Order progress' => 'Òrdugh adhartas','Display order progress from the theme' => 'Seall adhartas òrdugh bhon chuspair','Display the form field labels visible on the page' => 'Seall na leubail raon foirm a chithear air an duilleag','It is recommended to keep this option enabled for a better user experience.' => 'Thathas a’ moladh an roghainn seo a chumail comasach airson eòlas cleachdaiche nas fheàrr.','Theme ZK Nito' => 'Cuspair ZK Nito saor an asgaidh','Add extra fields to the checkout form' => 'Cuir raointean a bharrachd ris an fhoirm pàighidh','Adds an extra shipping email and shipping phone field to the shipping address section.' => 'Cuir post-d luingeis a bharrachd agus raon fòn luingeis ris an roinn seòladh luingeis.','Go to the home page' => 'Rach dhan duilleag-dhachaigh','Skip to content' => 'Rach gu susbaint','Create an account' => 'Cruthaich cunntas','Log in to your account' => 'Log a-steach don chunntas agad','Already have an account?' => 'A bheil cunntas agad mu thràth?','Logged in as %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Log out</a>' => 'Air logadh a-steach mar %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Log a-mach</a>','Your order has a total amount due of %s. No further payment is needed.' => 'Tha suim iomlan de %s aig an òrdugh agad ri phàigheadh. Chan eil feum air tuilleadh pàighidh.','Close and continue with checkout' => 'Dùin agus lean air adhart leis an àite-pàighidh','Continue' => 'Lean air adhart','Parcel terminal' => 'Terminal parsailean','<p>This widget has been replaced by Fluid Checkout. </p><p>When using Fluid Checkout, the checkout page needs to use the original WooCommerce shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> to work properly.</p><p>For more information, visit the Fluid Checkout documentation.</p>' => '<p>Chaidh Fluid Checkout a chuir na àite a’ widget seo.</p><p> Nuair a bhios tu a’ cleachdadh Fluid Checkout, feumaidh an duilleag pàighidh an shortcode tùsail WooCommerce <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> a chleachdadh gus obrachadh gu ceart.</p><p> Airson tuilleadh fiosrachaidh, tadhal air an Fluid Checkout sgrìobhainnean.</p>','Theme The7' => 'Cuspair The7','Additional header sections' => 'Earrannan cinn a bharrachd','Output additional header sections if enabled in the theme settings.' => 'Cuir a-mach earrannan cinn a bharrachd ma tha sin air a chomasachadh ann an roghainnean a’ chuspair.','Button label for applying coupon codesApply' => 'Cuir a-steach','Checkout step titleContact' => 'Cuir fios','Checkout step titleShipping' => 'Luingearachd','Checkout step titleBilling' => 'Bile','Checkout step titlePayment' => 'Pàigheadh','Checkout substep change link labelChange' => 'Atharraich','Checkout substep save link labelSave changes' => 'Sàbhail atharraichean','Substep review textNone.' => 'Chan eil gin.','Substep review field format%1$s' => '%1$s','Substep review field format: with label%2$s: %1$s' => '%2$s: %1$s','Image uploader.No image selected.' => 'Cha deach dealbh a thaghadh.','Settings sectionCart' => 'Cairt','Settings sectionOrder pay' => 'Òrdugh pàigheadh','Settings sectionThank you' => 'Tapadh leat','Settings section titleIntegrations' => 'Amalachaidhean','Settings section titleLicense keys' => 'Iuchraichean ceadachais','Captcha positionBefore place order section' => 'Ro earrann òrdugh àite','Captcha positionBefore place order button' => 'Putan òrdugh àite ro làimh','No shipping method chosen label for the order summary--' => '--','Close button aria-labelClose' => 'Dùin','Log in link label at checkout contact stepLog in' => 'Log a-steach','Log in separator label at for when guest checkout is disabledOr continue below' => 'No lean ort gu h-ìosal','Log in separator label at for when guest checkout is disabledOr continue as a guest' => 'No lean ort mar aoigh',] ];